<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>~/kinjal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="static/css/style.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/comic-mono@0.0.1/index.css"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/dejavu-sans-mono"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      ref="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <!-- <a href="" class="logo">~/kinjal</a> -->
      <a href="./" class="tlink">
        <span class="bracket">[</span>~/kinjal<span class="bracket">]</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="./posts" class="tlink">
          <span class="bracket">[</span>./posts<span class="bracket">]</span>
        </a>
        <a href="./projects" class="tlink">
          <span class="bracket">[</span>./projects<span class="bracket">]</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/static/kinjal-boro-resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="tlink">
          <span class="bracket">[</span>./resume<span class="bracket">]</span>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <section class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          kinjal<span class="sep">@</span>ricefield ~
          <span class="label">$</span> mefetch
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div class="neofetch">
            <pre class="neofetch-art">
                   ░
               ░  ░
              ░  ░
             ░    ░     ▄▀ ▄▀
              ░       ▄▀ ▄▀
              ▄▄█\█▄▄▀ ▄▀
         __▄`/█/`██`█▄▀__
       ▄▀·`.,█.██\-██/█`·▀▄
      ▐█▄██████,,████ .,▄▄█▌
      ▐▓▓▓▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▒▒░▌
      ▐▓▓▓▓▓▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒░░▌
       █▓▓▓▓▓▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒░░█
       ▐▓▓▓▓▓▓▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒░░░▌
        ▀█▓▓▓▓▓▒▒▒▒▒▒▒░░█▀
          ▀██▓▓▒▒▒▒▒▒██▀
             ▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀
            </pre>

            <div class="neofetch-info">
              <div class="row">
                <span class="label">name</span><span class="sep">&gt;</span>
                <span class="value">Kinjal Kavish Boro</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <span class="label">location</span><span class="sep">&gt;</span>
                <span class="value">Assam, India</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <span class="label">education</span
                ><span class="sep">&gt;</span>
                <span class="value">B.Tech Computer Science</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <span class="label">interests</span
                ><span class="sep">&gt;</span>
                <span class="value">Embedded systems, DevOps, Networking</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <span class="label">email</span><span class="sep">&gt;</span>
                <a href="mailto:borokinjalkavish@gmail.com" target="_blank" class="value email">
                  borokinjalkavish@gmail.com
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <span class="label">status</span><span class="sep">&gt;</span>
                {{ if eq .onlineStatus "online" }}
                  <span class="green-accent">online</span>
                {{ else }}
                  <span class="dim">offline</span>
                {{ end }}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="information">
        <h1>
          Hello, I am
          <span class="green-accent no-wrap">Kinjal Kavish Boro</span>
        </h1>
        <p>
          I am an undergraduate interested in building and experimenting with
          embedded systems, network architecture and backend development.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also love the ESP family of MCUs, Linux ricing and cooking food.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="projects-section">
        <h2>~/projects</h2>

        <div class="project-tree">
          <div class="tree-line">
            <span class="tree-prefix">| --> </span>
            <a href="https://github.com/localrice/EasyWiFi" target="_blank" class="project-link">EasyWifi</a>
            <span class="project-lang dim">C++</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tree-desc">
            Minimal WiFi manager for ESP8266 devices.
          </div>

          <div class="tree-line">
            <span class="tree-prefix">| --> </span>
            <a href="https://github.com/localrice/CITK-Notices-Notifier" target="_blank" class="project-link">CITK Notices Notifier</a>
            <span class="project-lang dim">Python</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tree-desc">
            A Telegram bot to send notifications regarding the notice board.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="links-section">
        <h2>~/links</h2>

        <div class="links-tree">
          <div class="tree-line">
            <span class="tree-prefix">| --> </span>
            <a href="https://github.com/localrice" target="_blank" class="link-item">
              github
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="tree-line">
            <span class="tree-prefix">| --> </span>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kinjal-kavish-boro-b014aa317/" target="_blank" class="link-item">
              linkedin
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>